# DCMAW Performance Testing Framework

This repository contains the performance test framework for testing DCMAW journeys.


## Required Installations

Pre-commit for running pre-commit hooks locally

```bash
brew install pre-commit && pre-commit install && pre-commit install -tprepare-commit-msg -tcommit-msg
```

k6 for testing and executing scripts locally
```bash
brew install k6
```

Install test dependencies
```bash
npm install
```


## Run Command
K6 environment variales can be found in test-mobile-journey.ts file.
Profile and scenario can be found in test.ts file.


```bash
# Generating dist files
npm start
```

```bash
# Run k6 test. Replace with actual values
k6 run ./dist/mobile/test.js -e PROFILE=profile_name -e SCENARIO=scenario_name -e MOBILE_TEST_CLIENT_EXECUTE_URL=test_client_execute_url -e MOBILE_BACK_END_URL=backend_url -e MOBILE_FRONT_END_URL=frontend_url -e MOBILE_BIOMETRIC_SESSION_ID=biometric_session_id
```